  "type": "spell",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You weave together threads of shadow to create a sword of solidified gloom in your hand. Strikes with the weapon are melee weapon attacks, but they use your spell attack modifier. On a hit, the target takes 2d8 points of spirit damage plus your spellcasting ability modifier. On a critical hit, the blade deals double damage. In addition, when you use the sword to attack a target that is in dim light or darkness, you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to the attack.</p>"
